#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.5:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Bālavagga "
msgstr "1. Fools "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Ayonisosutta "
msgstr "5. Improper "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.5:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo. "
msgstr "“A fool is known by three things. "

msgctxt "an3.5:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

# NOTE: Upagata in this sense i take as “staying close” i.e. “sticking to the point”, i.e. relevant.
msgctxt "an3.5:1.3"
msgid "Ayoniso pañhaṃ kattā hoti, ayoniso pañhaṃ vissajjetā hoti, parassa kho pana yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjitaṃ parimaṇḍalehi padabyañjanehi siliṭṭhehi upagatehi nābbhanumoditā hoti. "
msgstr "They ask a question improperly. They answer a question improperly. And when someone else answers a question properly—with well-rounded, coherent, and relevant words and phrases—they disagree with it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.5:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo. "
msgstr "These are the three things by which a fool is known. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.5:2.1"
msgid "Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo. "
msgstr "An astute person is known by three things. "

msgctxt "an3.5:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.5:2.3"
msgid "Yoniso pañhaṃ kattā hoti, yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjetā hoti, parassa kho pana yoniso pañhaṃ vissajjitaṃ parimaṇḍalehi padabyañjanehi siliṭṭhehi upagatehi abbhanumoditā hoti. "
msgstr "They ask a question properly. They answer a question properly. And when someone else answers a question properly—with well-rounded, coherent, and relevant words and phrases—they agree with it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.5:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito veditabbo. "
msgstr "These are the three things by which an astute person is known. "

msgctxt "an3.5:2.5"
msgid "Tasmātiha … pe …. "
msgstr "So you should train …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.5:2.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

